Specifically for the [[Template:Circle|Circle]] template, this is the way to include albums in a Circle's discography. Just as with Template:Circle, the staff of this wiki would like to thank [http://en.touhouwiki.net/wiki/Template:DiscographyItem TouhouWiki] for letting us use their template.
'''Note:''' It is very important that you reference the template without newlines.

== Usage ==
<pre>
{{DiscographyItem|Album name|Album cover art|Release date|Convention released at|Optional description|link=Optional}}
</pre>

== Parameters ==
;1
: The name of the album. If this is in japanese, don't forget to use <nowiki>{{</nowiki>[[Template:Lang|lang]]|ja<nowiki>}}</nowiki>.
: Also, if you use <nowiki>{{</nowiki>[[Template:Lang|lang]]|ja<nowiki>}}</nowiki>, you need to use the link parameter.
;2
: Cover art. Just the file name.
;3
: Release date in YYYY-MM-DD format.
;4
: Name of the convention the album was released at. Will automatically be linked.
;5
: An optional one-line description.
;link
: If the album title is in japanese, you must specify a link parameter with the name of the album sans <nowiki>{{</nowiki>[[Template:Lang|lang]]|ja<nowiki>}}</nowiki> template.